:Class FastJarvis
‚ćĚ FastAPI-like routing for Dyalog APL, built on top of Jarvis

    :Field Public  HandlersNS    ‚ćĚ namespace containing handler functions; set before Start
    :Field Private _routes       ‚ćĚ vector of route descriptor namespaces
    :Field public _jarvis        ‚ćĚ underlying Jarvis instance


    ‚ąá Make routes;pairs
      :Access Public
      :Implements constructor
      HandlersNS‚Üź()
      _routes‚Üź‚ć¨
      _jarvis‚Üź‚ć¨
      :If 0<‚ćīroutes
          _RegisterPair¬®routes    ‚ćĚ each element is ‚äā('METHOD /path' 'handlerName')
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Make0;pairs
      :Access Public
